    </h1>
    <p>
      One last step: choose the pages you want to manage with Gorgias.
      <br />
      If you just wanted to re-activate your Facebook integration or update your permissions: it's done, you can leave this page.
    </p>
    <form
      class=""
    >
      <div
        class="mb-4"
      >
        <p
          class="font-weight-medium"
        >
          We found 
          1
           pages associated with your account. Please activate the pages you want to use with Gorgias:
        </p>
        <div
          class="mb-2"
        >
          <div
            class="page"
          >
            <div
              class="d-flex flex-wrap flex-md-nowrap"
            >
